title: "Reasoning Segmentation for Images and Videos: A Survey"
collection: publications
category: manuscripts
permalink: /publication/rsiv
excerpt: 'Reasoning Segmentation (RS) segments objects from natural-language queries that require reasoning and knowledge, moving beyond fixed categories or explicit prompts. This survey synthesizes 26 methods, evaluation metrics, and 29 datasets/benchmarks, reviews applications across domains, and outlines current gaps and future research directions.'
